<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Each &#x27e8;keyword&#x27e9; is an identifier, each &#x27e8;transformer spec&#x27e9; is an instance of <font face="Courier">syntax-rules</font>, and &#x27e8;body&#x27e9; is a sequence of one or more definitions followed by one or more expressions.&#xa0;
