  <body>
    <p>
      Similarly, in a &#x27e8;body&#x27e9;, <font face="Courier">(begin </font>&#x27e8;definition1&#x27e9; ...<font face="Courier">)</font>&#xa0; is equivalent to the sequence &#x27e8;definition1 &#x27e9; ... .
