</html></richcontent>
<node CREATED="1375076383774" ID="ID_1492220165" MODIFIED="1375076393859" TEXT="&#x2022;">
<node CREATED="1375076425660" ID="ID_1145884414" MODIFIED="1375154672259" TEXT="&#x27e8;name&#x27e9; is bound to a representation of the record type itself. "/>
<node CREATED="1375154672260" ID="ID_131539528" MODIFIED="1375154701518" TEXT="This may be ">
<node CREATED="1375154701518" ID="ID_227721968" MODIFIED="1375154709151" TEXT="a run-time object "/>
<node CREATED="1375154709151" ID="ID_1757067803" MODIFIED="1375154709153" TEXT="or a purely syntactic representation. "/>
</node>
<node CREATED="1375154680081" ID="ID_1916967574" MODIFIED="1375154687949" TEXT="The representation is not utilized in this report, but it serves as a means to identify the record type for use by further language extensions."/>
</node>
<node CREATED="1375076394325" ID="ID_1357002353" MODIFIED="1375076395467" TEXT="&#x2022;">
<node CREATED="1375076433035" ID="ID_1274963958" MODIFIED="1375154767929">
<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &#x27e8;constructor name&#x27e9; is bound to a procedure that takes as many arguments as there are &#x27e8;field name&#x27e9;s in the <font face="Courier">(</font>&#x27e8;constructor name&#x27e9; ... <font face="Courier">)</font>&#xa0;subexpression and returns a new record of type &#x27e8;name&#x27e9;.&#xa0;
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
<node CREATED="1375154733362" ID="ID_606573730" MODIFIED="1375154773130" TEXT="Fields whose names are listed with &#x27e8;constructor name&#x27e9; have the corresponding argument as their initial value. "/>
<node CREATED="1375154773132" ID="ID_618611742" MODIFIED="1375154777697" TEXT="The initial values of all other fields are unspecified. "/>
<node CREATED="1375154777697" ID="ID_100851116" MODIFIED="1375154777699" TEXT="It is an error for a field name to appear in &#x27e8;constructor&#x27e9; but not as a &#x27e8;field name&#x27e9;."/>
</node>
<node CREATED="1375076395837" ID="ID_1061139851" MODIFIED="1375076397244" TEXT="&#x2022;">
<node CREATED="1375076439555" ID="ID_1312467445" MODIFIED="1375156375251">
<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      &#x27e8;pred&#x27e9; is bound to a predicate that returns <font face="Courier">#t</font>&#xa0;when given a value returned by the procedure bound to &#x27e8;constructor name&#x27e9; and <font face="Courier">#f</font>&#xa0; for everything else.
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node CREATED="1375076397573" ID="ID_433553836" MODIFIED="1375076398708" TEXT="&#x2022;">
<node CREATED="1375076444682" ID="ID_1630891710" MODIFIED="1375156427083" TEXT="Each &#x27e8;accessor name&#x27e9; is bound to a procedure that takes a record of type &#x27e8;name&#x27e9; and returns the current value of the corresponding field. "/>
<node CREATED="1375156427085" ID="ID_1272064167" MODIFIED="1375156427087" TEXT="It is an error to pass an accessor a value which is not a record of the appropriate type."/>
</node>
<node CREATED="1375076398925" ID="ID_43181648" MODIFIED="1375076400033" TEXT="&#x2022;">
<node CREATED="1375076449922" ID="ID_680282381" MODIFIED="1375156442998" TEXT="Each &#x27e8;modifier name&#x27e9; is bound to a procedure that takes a record of type &#x27e8;name&#x27e9; and a value which becomes the new value of the corresponding field; an unspecified value is returned. "/>
<node CREATED="1375156442999" ID="ID_1625069417" MODIFIED="1375156443001" TEXT="It is an error to pass a modifier a first argument which is not a record of the appropriate type."/>
</node>
</node>
</node>
<node CREATED="1375083628203" ID="ID_203864946" MODIFIED="1375083632899" TEXT="&#xb6; 7">
<node CREATED="1375083638085" ID="ID_381551868" MODIFIED="1375083638616" TEXT="For instance, the following record-type definition"/>
<node CREATED="1375083643666" ID="ID_1672176019" MODIFIED="1375156559066">
