<node CREATED="1377582222256" ID="ID_1731230182" MODIFIED="1377583737552" TEXT="A program can use a global variable definition to bind any variable. "/>
<node CREATED="1377583737552" ID="ID_761259079" MODIFIED="1377583742838" TEXT="It may subsequently alter any such binding by an assignment (see section 4.1.6). "/>
