</html></richcontent>
</node>
</node>
</node>
<node CREATED="1379179719895" ID="ID_640390194" MODIFIED="1379179720631" TEXT="&#xb6; 3">
<node CREATED="1379179726230" ID="ID_1342468743" MODIFIED="1379220598150" TEXT="These numerical type predicates can be applied to any kind of argument, including non-numbers. "/>
<node CREATED="1379220598150" ID="ID_906666439" MODIFIED="1379220631130">
<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      They return <font face="Courier">#t</font>&#xa0;if the object is of the named type, and otherwise they return <font face="Courier">#f</font>.
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
<node CREATED="1379220631132" ID="ID_1104530009" MODIFIED="1379220631136">
<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      In general, if a type predicate is true of a number then all higher type predicates are also true of that number.&#xa0;
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
<node CREATED="1379220605961" ID="ID_838752708" MODIFIED="1379220605962" TEXT="Consequently, if a type predicate is false of a number, then all lower type predicates are also false of that number."/>
</node>
<node CREATED="1379179727342" ID="ID_433830806" MODIFIED="1379179728478" TEXT="&#xb6;&#xa0;4">
<node CREATED="1379179732351" ID="ID_174944" MODIFIED="1379220677382">
<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      If <i>z</i>&#xa0;is a complex number, then <font face="Courier">(real? </font><i>z</i><font face="Courier">)</font>&#xa0;is true if and only if <font face="Courier">(zero? (imag-part </font><i>z</i><font face="Courier">))</font>&#xa0;is true.
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
<node CREATED="1379220677385" ID="ID_1757391347" MODIFIED="1379220732172">
<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      If <i>x</i>&#xa0;is an inexact real number, then <font face="Courier">(integer? </font><i>x</i><font face="Courier">)</font>&#xa0; is true if and only if <font face="Courier">(= </font><i>x</i>&#xa0;<font face="Courier">(round </font><i>x</i><font face="Courier">))</font>.
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
</node>
<node CREATED="1379179734630" ID="ID_488414384" MODIFIED="1379179735526" TEXT="&#xb6;&#xa0;5">
<node CREATED="1379179740133" ID="ID_8138989" MODIFIED="1379220760208">
<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      The numbers <font face="Courier">+inf.0</font>, <font face="Courier">-inf.0</font>, and <font face="Courier">+nan.0</font>&#xa0;are real but not rational.
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
