<node CREATED="1377915880441" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_123388790" MODIFIED="1378221253847" TEXT="&#xb6; 1">
<node CREATED="1377915882868" ID="ID_1911307778" MODIFIED="1377917953630">
<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      The standard boolean objects for true and false are written as <font face="Courier">#t</font>&#xa0; and <font face="Courier">#f</font>.&#xa0;
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
<node CREATED="1377916848187" ID="ID_897895813" MODIFIED="1377917971396">
<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Alternatively, they can be written <font face="Courier">#true</font>&#xa0;and <font face="Courier">#false</font>, respectively.&#xa0;
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
<node CREATED="1377916852990" ID="ID_448860478" MODIFIED="1377919439247">
<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      What really matters, though, are the objects that the Scheme conditional expressions (<font face="Courier">if</font>, <font face="Courier">cond</font>, <font face="Courier">and</font>, <font face="Courier">or</font>, <font face="Courier">when</font>, unless, <font face="Courier">do</font>) treat as true or false.&#xa0;
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
<node CREATED="1377916859483" ID="ID_109404022" MODIFIED="1377916859485" TEXT="The phrase &#x201c;a true value&#x201d; (or sometimes just &#x201c;true&#x201d;) means any object treated as true by the conditional expressions, and the phrase &#x201c;a false value&#x201d; (or &#x201c;false&#x201d;) means any object treated as false by the conditional expressions."/>
</node>
<node CREATED="1377915889856" FOLDED="true" ID="ID_1612323384" MODIFIED="1378221259006" TEXT="&#xb6;&#xa0;2">
<node CREATED="1377915891677" ID="ID_1309063243" MODIFIED="1377919464228">
<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Of all the Scheme values, only <font face="Courier">#f</font>&#xa0;counts as false in conditional expressions.&#xa0;
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
<node CREATED="1377916877742" ID="ID_128812171" MODIFIED="1377919475984">
<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      All other Scheme values, including <font face="Courier">#t</font>, count as true.
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
</node>
