  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      The <font face="Courier">char-downcase</font>&#xa0;procedure, given an argument that is the uppercase part of a Unicode casing pair, returns the lowercase member of the pair, provided that both characters are supported by the Scheme implementation.&#xa0;
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
<node CREATED="1378013227285" ID="ID_1534931983" MODIFIED="1378013227288" TEXT="Note that language-sensitive casing pairs are not used. If the argument is not the uppercase member of such a pair, it is returned."/>
