</html></richcontent>
</node>
</node>
</node>
<node CREATED="1378527727031" ID="ID_288948512" MODIFIED="1378527730603" TEXT="&#xb6; 45">
<node CREATED="1378527730604" ID="ID_601495267" MODIFIED="1378565973661">
<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      Calls its <i>producer</i>&#xa0;argument with no arguments and a continuation that, when passed some values, calls the <i>consumer</i>&#xa0;procedure with those values as arguments.
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
<node CREATED="1378565973664" ID="ID_1851041153" MODIFIED="1378565973669">
<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      The continuation for the call to <i>consumer</i>&#xa0; is the continuation of the call to <font face="Courier">call-with-values</font>.
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
</node>
