<node CREATED="1378222549298" ID="ID_672664337" MODIFIED="1378567913634" TEXT="This section describes Scheme&#x2019;s exception-handling and exception-raising procedures. "/>
<node CREATED="1378567913634" ID="ID_898436179" LINK="#ID_332841546" MODIFIED="1378567941823" TEXT="For the concept of Scheme exceptions, see section 1.3.2. "/>
<node CREATED="1378567920226" ID="ID_485842347" LINK="#ID_733376236" MODIFIED="1378567960478" TEXT="See also 4.2.7 for the guard syntax."/>
