<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      If <i>proc</i>&#xa0;returns, then the port is closed automatically and the values yielded by the <i>proc</i>&#xa0;are returned.&#xa0;
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
<node CREATED="1378874800752" ID="ID_597601022" MODIFIED="1378876799731">
<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      If proc <i>does</i>&#xa0;not return, then the port must not be closed automatically unless it is possible to prove that the port will never again be used for a read or write operation.
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
