<richcontent TYPE="NODE"><html>
  <head>
    
  </head>
  <body>
    <p>
      All Scheme implementations must permit the escape sequence <font face="Courier">\x&lt;hexdigits&gt;;</font>&#xa0; to appear in Scheme identifiers that are enclosed in vertical lines.&#xa0;
    </p>
  </body>
</html></richcontent>
</node>
<node CREATED="1379394751346" ID="ID_1719593417" MODIFIED="1379394751347" TEXT="If the character with the given Unicode scalar value is supported by the implementation, identifiers containing such a sequence are equivalent to identifiers containing the corresponding character."/>
